overview: Sharmoofers and Afroto battle it out on stage, leaving it up to the audience as per Sound Clash tradition, to cheer their hearts out and vote in favour of their favourite artists.From Afroto’s catchy and cheeky bars to Sharmoofers’s Afro-inspired ballads, the upcoming Red Bull Soundclash seems to feature yet another genre-bending experience, since their last gig in 2019.
title: Red Bull SoundClash 2023 - Sharmoofers & Afroto
